Description: Get the most out of your vacation rentals with HomeEscape. No booking fees. No communication restrictions.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: HomeEscape, based in Miami, Florida, was born from a single idea: why should people have to pay expensive fees when advertising their vacation rental? Or, why should travelers pay unnecessary fees to book their property? HomeEscape’s platform allows users to search and book properties without being required to pay fees to use HomeEscape. Through HomeEscape, property managers and owners offer a large selection of vacation homes with extensive amenities, including more space to relax and enjoy their stay, at a fraction of the cost of traditional resort accommodations. HomeEscape offers its users a comprehensive suite of tools for booking properties, making online payments, reviewing property performance, and getting situational and technical support. With new features being developed every day, HomeEscape offers a world-class alternative to the impersonal property listing sites and travel aggregators that crowd the market today. With no disincentive to join, HomeEscape has been expanding at a rapid rate, quickly becoming one of the most sought after vacation rental sites this year.
